      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/japan-s-love-of-foreign-stocks-risks-pushing-the-yen-even-lower</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本散户投资者对海外股票的热衷进一步打压日元，并增加了唐纳德·特朗普的关税和与美国的巨大利差带来的下行风险。]]></description>
